---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Suscríbete — Miranda Urban"
  description="Recibe un aviso cada vez que publique algo nuevo. Sin spam, solo libros."
>

  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="header-left">
      <p class="eyebrow">✦ Quedémonos en contacto</p>
      <h1 class="page-title">Suscríbete</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="header-right">
      <p class="header-desc">
        Cada vez que publique una reseña o una nota nueva, te mando un aviso.
        Sin spam, sin algoritmos — solo un email cuando haya algo nuevo que leer.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="subscribe-wrap">

    <div class="subscribe-left">
      <p class="promise-title">Qué esperar</p>
      <ul class="promise-list">
        <li>Un email cuando publique algo nuevo</li>
        <li>Sin frecuencia forzada — publico cuando tengo algo que decir</li>
        <li>Sin publicidad ni contenido patrocinado</li>
        <li>Te puedes dar de baja cuando quieras</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="subscribe-right">
      <form
        action="https://buttondown.com/api/emails/embed-subscribe/mirandaurban"
        method="post"
        target="popupwindow"
        onsubmit="window.open('https://buttondown.com/mirandaurban','popupwindow')"
        class="subscribe-form"
      >
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="bd-email" class="form-label">Tu correo electrónico</label>
          <div class="form-row">
            <input
              type="email"
              name="email"
              id="bd-email"
              placeholder="tu@correo.com"
              required
              class="form-input"
            />
            <button type="submit" class="form-btn">Suscribirme →</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="form-note">
          Al suscribirte aceptas recibir emails ocasionales de Miranda Urban.
          Puedes darte de baja en cualquier momento.
        </p>
      </form>
    </div>

  </div>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    padding: 5rem 3rem 3rem;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: end;
    border-bottom: var(--border);
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rust);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 5.5rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .header-desc {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-weight: 300;
    max-width: 40ch;
  }

  /* ── CONTENIDO ── */
  .subscribe-wrap {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    border-bottom: var(--border);
  }

  .subscribe-left {
    padding: 4rem 3rem;
    border-right: var(--border);
  }

  .promise-title {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: rgba(44,44,42,0.4);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .promise-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .promise-list li {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .promise-list li::before {
    content: '✦';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    font-size: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--rust);
    top: 0.35rem;
  }

  /* ── FORMULARIO ── */
  .subscribe-right {
    padding: 4rem 3rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .subscribe-form {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .form-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: rgba(44,44,42,0.5);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .form-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .form-input {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    border: var(--border);
    border-right: none;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--ink);
    outline: none;
    border-radius: 0;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .form-input::placeholder {
    color: rgba(44,44,42,0.3);
  }

  .form-input:focus {
    border-color: var(--rust);
  }

  .form-btn {
    padding: 0.85rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--cream);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    border: var(--border);
    border-color: var(--ink);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    white-space: nowrap;
    border-radius: 0;
  }

  .form-btn:hover {
    background: var(--rust);
    border-color: var(--rust);
  }

  .form-note {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.07em;
    color: rgba(44,44,42,0.3);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(14px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .eyebrow      { animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease both; }
  .page-title   { animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease 0.08s both; }
  .header-desc  { animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease 0.16s both; }
  .subscribe-wrap { animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease 0.24s both; }
</style>